align-center\" id=\"SE-f86c7776-22d1-4351-a8f3-bf9df3f837dc\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-74943b41-289b-45bf-8ce1-3d906a951829\" style=\"color:#555555;\">데이터를 접수하실 때</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-6a2b8f3b-89fe-40c1-a806-ba114e64fbe1\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-151f7d7c-a872-4e90-83b9-c0094eb13178\" style=\"color:#555555;\">반드시 레스터라이징,</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-5784c9ba-4d89-4d42-a8ab-cb480ac8703c\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-7861c3cb-611f-4025-82fb-b46aa4d67f54\" style=\"color:#555555;\">아웃라인, 곡선처리를</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-ccc5042d-c2a3-4d75-9249-6cb3a5455d48\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-3048495f-57d3-4576-a21e-c68f9ed006e4\" style=\"color:#555555;\">해주셔야 작업이 가능합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-8ffb1025-5534-4127-a0f6-b2971c1f8844\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\" style=\"max-width:406px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223769569649/002.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-e18b47e2-84e2-4f4c-a084-4f75920677f9\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-b045ed12-7f2b-4847-bfba-949f4ab49e43\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-34878441-65da-48d5-87f9-c31dc85af583\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>이미지 해상도</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-ae320b77-d426-4e82-bb94-7850b0b10f19\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-fb6a4fa0-48a1-4eb8-9857-8d2e9fdcfae3\" style=\"color:#555555;\">디자인에 포함된 이미지의 해상도가</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-268f025b-4a60-44bf-8444-0964255111c1\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-f6c71696-acb9-48b5-8df0-e63f81014484\" style=\"color:#555555;\">현저히 낮으면 작업 시에</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-3b82859d-a9ba-4926-bcc8-62acf1bb1eb3\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-db4e178d-331d-46b8-9085-72fe2d5c5cff\" style=\"color:#555555;\">깔끔하게 인쇄되지 않습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-03ab33c7-a349-45e9-9bcc-3892c7081d7d\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-0b6542b2-6543-44f6-8200-5a9a74ce9b36\" style=\"color:#555555;\">반드시 이미지 해상도는 300dpi</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-704fa3ec-3f64-4440-8f87-efdd0c42fc16\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e7430af7-0fd4-4b46-a07c-57aeedc3cf12\" style=\"color:#555555;\">이상으로 작업을 하시기 바랍니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-52d4240c-9712-4164-8f02-499af916a187\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-c9b6550d-fa6a-48b3-9531-93e6d8cbfffa\" style=\"color:#555555;\">간혹 낮은 해상도를 올리면 안 되냐는</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-8e8c3a43-c01f-4e96-9e28-e3baa8203ffb\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-201ae51b-0275-4019-b0ff-7fbec505c250\" style=\"color:#555555;\">문의가 많습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-1c9ddb5a-6be5-4e30-bdc0-05d9ab8285e3\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-c013c642-eae6-4055-9697-2d62e444167d\" style=\"color:#555555;\">원본이 낮으면 해상도를 올리다고</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-0efff4ea-8a67-45f8-b663-68f878072716\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e560a98b-0670-4d01-b1fe-04e68cd6fd2b\" style=\"color:#555555;\">좋아지지 않으니 참고하세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-861280db-46ce-444d-9c64-62408430f44f\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\" style=\"max-width:310px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223769569649/003.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-80fe893c-1428-4259-ae38-7e27e34ffe54\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-c38004ba-956e-4a5c-9022-33e6d048b288\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-8aaf0f6f-fbf9-4868-a7b6-bbdc76a95759\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>색상 문제</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-252d968b-16b3-44ec-9b6b-e459d4086bb6\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a323f902-9066-4099-9bb3-64a51e59eafd\" style=\"color:#555555;\">디자인에 포함된 모든 색상은</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-c13c568f-ac35-4251-9d5d-c2e12fea1376\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-da3e16ac-5158-4bb1-a260-9d45247c4a3c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">CMYK 모드여야 합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-acb231ce-7df6-44bd-a351-5166ab7dd3d9\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-098e8b84-8010-40f1-af70-c92d5816b45d\" style=\"color:#555555;\">RGB나 별색을 사용하시면</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-f437067f-a388-46be-9a11-5a1814cde581\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-c0499b47-0856-4726-a424-d53302f7aafd\" style=\"color:#555555;\">색상이 바뀌어 인쇄될 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-a43b6382-2a87-4e3a-bb6a-452978879033\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-cf135b27-af91-4c67-9679-c5e73f958c7f\" style=\"color:#555555;\">색상이 바뀐다는 말은 의도된</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-9b7c1039-8d3b-4820-a14c-5c1e19e4c774\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-aa06fa47-e799-4871-a29b-ceee9fe7cad8\" style=\"color:#555555;\">색상보다 어둡게 나오거나</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-f8c8064a-c748-48ea-9936-6995c33326ad\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-45c6a667-0575-4d63-a212-f47581597a04\" style=\"color:#555555;\">별색인 경우</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-0966b0a1-f353-40dd-9c0e-efb7e1775848\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-df2dc144-0877-4185-9aba-545873de3e58\" style=\"color:#555555;\">색상이 유실되는 경우까지 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-d6b4191f-ac8c-4034-9339-93958d78da21\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-2004a724-f768-468a-92aa-d2f73172bd93\" style=\"color:#555555;\">반드시 CMYK 모드로</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-5179283f-5275-4b96-afa3-f1cb9ff55f38\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-ddfc23f0-cc09-484d-9c9a-b97d830672f5\" style=\"color:#555555;\">모든 개체를 사용하세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-e05645c9-2790-4617-92d8-2b5be65dab22\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e3cab693-bfad-489d-9344-87292905e02d\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-84193577-ccd0-47df-9d00-fe9b1eed23ea\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-9857b858-b668-40d1-ba69-dff9a892b234\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><a class=\"se-link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"text\" href=\"https://blog.naver.com/cookthedesign/222895566635\" target=\"_blank\">https://blog.naver.com/(주)파파스컴퍼니/222895566635</a></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-4a04bf24-98af-4e19-9e9d-b0a0a6a3b3b9\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-a647cd01-4361-4949-a6be-3561cb048a55\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-100ef3d3-6e22-4c10-b7bd-71d5d6b8587e\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-d51aedd9-8570-4695-8286-da0f928ddfd7\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-7dfcbf2a-9255-47f4-b8db-529558e6f43b\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>2. 반드시 선입금이어야 합니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-4da1d980-f92a-40fd-bdb1-17ace086815b\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi s