1-9c067025cde2\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\"><b>데이터가 인쇄용으로</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-81fc67ee-2f5f-4b1b-86e2-5a55b714a8d1\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-50c6a713-cf21-4a2f-8c44-6e0b47e8e294\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\"><b>적합한 경우에만</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-06c20c30-17bd-4fce-a7c1-55a66852a308\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-0adddefb-e998-457f-a401-113b62e48a13\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\"><b>당일 택배 발송이 가능합니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-dc9978a0-1b14-4418-89b0-a548c5277f20\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-2da37ae4-7860-4f7e-b545-363e4ecf4f33\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-2a80d65a-7aa1-4d54-80a2-7eb3b74feee5\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-7d9b8509-1ed3-406f-bc46-7dfdbc823270\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>3. 조건에 맞는 사양이어야 합니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-7b829b8d-0976-4c55-8702-05c7ace4c89a\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-c6c62c5e-56c3-4157-9339-16aebd25e175\" style=\"color:#555555;\">당일 배송은 디지털 인쇄가 기본입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-528a4f5a-52f4-4d6f-bb54-8797eda2b6d2\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d17ecb6a-c787-4dd1-8d2e-5fbe09ef5e42\" style=\"color:#555555;\">디지털 인쇄 특성상</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-dbe5ee0a-00db-4b67-8eda-16619bf5a7f5\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-6f1a4c16-52d4-4d3f-80f2-b9ef2430740b\" style=\"color:#555555;\">가능한 사이즈, 가능한 종이,</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-64228da1-e712-4e35-acb1-75e21b65c3fc\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-c26b0f11-531f-4ca0-a201-c2d4f92c7d46\" style=\"color:#555555;\">가능한 인쇄 방식이 존재합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-1595866d-757f-47e7-af8c-8e9aba59afb1\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-81c1d631-0b75-4727-a3a8-737d3d3c2ff8\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-6fc84fef-3907-4dbd-9680-a2a386c4eb5a\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-1b1cd3e7-990d-400e-9bc0-a6959815f0cf\" style=\"color:#555555;\">다음 사항에 맞는지 확인 후 문의하세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-bebc7372-380d-4869-a529-1a9dec153d09\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-437318f1-33a0-4fcb-a86b-83b43f11fe82\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_line\" id=\"SE-1798d225-2758-4181-9bcb-33f6a7c9f762\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_line\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f03254aa-610b-46a6-95eb-dcbf562cbc8f\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-de5b52b3-341c-4eaa-a82a-7e3a690dff52\" style=\"\">사이즈</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-42ce6175-7ee7-4aae-bc93-9ad7bf575a59\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-939f4476-5965-43d0-b2be-5ebb5b383900\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-aa6a92c5-3bfb-44b9-af79-9c5b8a9e7a90\" style=\"color:#555555;\">당일 배송이 되려면 디지털 인쇄 사이즈에 포함되어야 합니다. 가능한 사이즈는 다음과 같습니다. 이외의 사이즈는 불가능합니다. 참고해 주세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-2a8500fe-f6c5-4bbb-b44a-1ecddb1416e7\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223769569649/004.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-4a2893d0-c7e4-4cb7-94c1-a4e07b10a2bb\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-dd937135-8fbf-431f-be5d-f556d64d6a93\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-936260a5-f426-4b8f-982b-7934bad8402d\" style=\"color:#555555;\">B2 사이즈인 46 2절 안에 들어와야 가능합니다. 이 범위를 벗어나는 포스터인 경우는 대량생산을 가능하지만 디지털 소량 인쇄는 불가능합니다. 참고하세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b2b3d434-b993-43ca-a282-70b351435460\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e3c427c4-afd5-492a-802b-b11f672b802e\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-71b361cd-9754-4006-ad7e-7f434440adf3\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-14539606-6f70-4c81-95a2-0251a516a823\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\"><b>최대 인쇄사이즈 : 508mm × 738mm</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e4a64a68-8ba6-4964-8fee-9856a15d13d4\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-819231c9-3b1e-4bb9-ae82-f57a1c391415\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_line\" id=\"SE-350c8782-3257-4970-b0ba-f7681b004895\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_line\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-0c5aaefb-d746-437b-aa5e-fc4af9965dfd\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-6a28da64-6bc6-4ab3-abbc-0775071d27dd\" style=\"\">종이</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-6cb28535-7284-4d7c-abf3-77bd9015eb2f\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-2831f7c7-cfd8-4396-9fc1-1d195d2f4db7\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-0e7e36e8-0b35-4565-8f50-3518e9352bb4\" style=\"color:#555555;\">용지도 일반적인 아트지나 스노우지는 가능하지만 특별한 수입용지를 사용해야 되는 경우는 당일 배송이 불가능할 수 있습니다. 종이는 반드시 상담을 통해 가능한 종이를 추천 받으시기 바랍니다. 하지만 기본적으로 가능한 종이는 다음과 같습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-5aa7f19c-357e-44c9-bc8c-4d81a182bbec\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-c6161a3f-599d-4405-9858-69e3107c1ff5\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f835b620-8c4d-4cc3-82ce-5245c7ea26a3\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-d7cd1626-fdc2-4f6d-8889-a684a018d9a1\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\"><b>일반 아트지/스노우지/모조지 계열</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-edc3eb3c-aeec-4c28-8195-e50cfd1d9e3f\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-1f5a25c5-e72e-4578-8631-f49ead6886e8\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\"><b>고급지 중에 랑데뷰, 아르떼, 반누브 종이</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e9c66bcd-72d7-44cd-a8c5-03c465fe1479\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-84cf9eee-1676-4c9e-815d-3d83e97a4022\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\"><b>기타 색지 일부</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-9134145e-c35c-470c-ac71-dc3901ec6ed4\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-33