-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-dd1ee43e-86bd-48be-8050-86f42e5d4dc7\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ba73d8ce-3c74-4605-9583-ec3bb80da8fc\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-bc68eb45-cf55-47a9-aa7b-5c8b8d513f92\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\"><b>당일 출고는 재단만 가능합니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-1444f38a-d519-40de-baf2-b621154c6707\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-4a2d825a-a4ff-4f88-bb84-95559586b3f7\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_line\" id=\"SE-9c4f14c5-660c-4103-abc1-54c09208ff12\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_line\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-532d4ba3-5002-4400-8c47-1afab7d7a2d0\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-5cfa5902-8026-4f8e-91df-ca305eee2ca2\" style=\"\">수량</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-32903cc5-eacf-477b-9c55-520040b195b1\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a27b01f4-c0b4-4cf7-8a8a-19fd2f0658ba\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-0f5ff6d2-a192-4fb1-beda-73d48bdf811a\" style=\"color:#555555;\">기본 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-b615b52c-464f-4355-98ea-7bf9a4178589\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>200장</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-be424805-fbf9-4aa4-9d07-1c5afb52f00c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">까지는 가능하지만 이 상의 경우는 생산이 불가능하다기보다는 오프셋보다 단가가 비쌀질 수 있습니다. 이점을 참고하시고 판단해서 주문하시면 됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f7f3d9a0-e442-4c9d-832c-05d8e181d854\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-0433879b-fb79-4da2-93f5-481332b6b56c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-cacc987d-3962-4f50-a5c4-ff45d400da11\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-ded551f9-3b60-4758-8d8a-1722cdb901f9\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\"><b>수량은 200장 미만</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-03268ef5-fbbb-4adc-a80a-1700d33587c1\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-18e06a98-ad18-4f38-91c5-b33d9809f044\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b72777c1-108e-473a-8c8f-96adc367814c\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-c8918554-eadc-4dc5-a12a-5a9d06e42eb9\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-talktalk se-l-default\" id=\"SE-1418b90c-befd-4fc1-8b9e-69500b0bf9bc\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-talktalk se-section-align-center se-l-default\">\n<a class=\"se-module se-module-talktalk\" href=\"https://talk.naver.com/w4tbeb?frm=mblog&amp;ref=https%3A%2F%2Fm.blog.naver.com%2Fcookthedesign%2F223769569649#nafullscreen\